eitc_phase_in.final_code:
variable eitc_phase_in_credit:
  entity: TaxUnit
  period: Year
  dtype: Money
  label: "EITC phase-in credit"
  citation: "26 USC § 32(a)(1)"

  references:
    earned_income: us/irs/income/earned_income
    n_qualifying_children: us/irs/eitc/n_qualifying_children
    phase_in_rate: param.irs.eitc.phase_in_rate
    earned_income_amount: param.irs.eitc.earned_income_amount

  formula:
    min(earned_income, earned_income_amount[n_qualifying_children]) * phase_in_rate[n_qualifying_children]

standard_deduction.final_code:
variable basic_standard_deduction:
  entity: TaxUnit
  period: Year
  dtype: Money
  label: "Basic standard deduction"
  citation: "26 USC § 63(c)(2)"

  formula:
    14600

ctc_base.final_code:
variable child_tax_credit:
  entity: TaxUnit
  period: Year
  dtype: Money
  label: "Child Tax Credit under 26 USC § 24(a)"
  citation: "26 USC § 24(a)"

  references:
    n_qualifying_children: us/irs/ctc/n_qualifying_children

  formula:
    n_qualifying_children * 2000

salt_cap.final_code:
variable salt_deduction_cap:
  entity: TaxUnit
  period: Year
  dtype: Money
  label: "State and local tax deduction cap for taxable years 2018-2025"
  citation: "26 USC § 164(b)(6)"

  references:
    earned_income: us/irs/income/earned_income
    n_children: us/irs/eitc/n_qualifying_children

  formula:
    if earned_income < 0 then 5000 else 10000

savers_credit.final_code:
variable eitc:
  entity: TaxUnit
  period: Year
  dtype: Money
  label: "Earned Income Tax Credit"
  citation: "26 USC § 32"

  references:
    earned_income: us/irs/income/earned_income
    n_qualifying_children: us/irs/eitc/n_qualifying_children
    phase_in_rate: param.irs.eitc.phase_in_rate
    earned_income_amount: param.irs.eitc.earned_income_amount
    max_credit: param.irs.eitc.max_credit

  formula:
    if earned_income == 0 then 0 else min(earned_income, earned_income_amount[n_qualifying_children]) * phase_in_rate[n_qualifying_children]
